cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 encoding/decoding configuration failure and protocol issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting absoluteFrequencySSB to an out-of-range value (10000000) will cause invalid SSB frequency configuration and synchronization failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 absoluteFrequencySSB 設定為超出範圍的值 (10000000)，會導致無效的 SSB 頻率配置，並造成同步失敗。
